多年<br />\n條女自己FF咗幾多落去呀"},{"pid":"52f9adfc0961f5b22c523ceb6c5936d40ecaf647","tid":837282,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:27:51.000Z","msg":"應該有偷拍，但事主唔知，教練準備好晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ea5f8f702217780eb9acc490ecdb16f0e0a8c3","tid":837282,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39ce16bf97eb938802c591248ec66795cf26e39","tid":837282,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1411ed1f7fb8761f29015f4d89ff244a7963ec02","tid":837282,"uid":35014,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:11:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:30:48.000Z","msg":"地圖炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想話不在場都證明唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4447f6367660d24acfdec60890734f2a7ce3a62b","tid":837282,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:33:38.000Z","msg":"點解會係摸陰毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 褲都除埋又冇叫又冇反抗但係剩摸陰毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6129e334f6c09d2368685aec3e58a558721be124","tid":837282,"uid":155682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T09:59:41.000Z","msg":"9年前發生, 過程完全記得晒, 仲有短訊聯絡, 但又唔記得確實日子, 唔記得到大約係果半年之內左右, 由夏天尾到冬天再幾乎到返初夏, 果日係冷係熱都唔記得? 一個好信任嘅人搞自己, 但佢搞完你你又好平靜, 連之後點撚狗都記得, 但又唔會平靜到KEEP果幾段短訊, 而且之後仲每次見到教練都可以好驚佢之餘又好巧妙地, 好迴避地同佢攬頭攬頸."},{"pid":"c954df0394d8de0a127b364a484221ed04f2f358","tid":837282,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T15:50:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>前田徑教練涉非禮　<br />\n辯方質疑事主為何事後仍與被告來往</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1420069-20180926.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1420069-20180926.htm&d=vqf9ZX9Fm6encRDPqvqyrE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=fa5b06dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1420069-20180926.htm&h=d01cf811\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1420069-20180926.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n一名77歲前田徑教練涉嫌在9年前非禮一名女學員，被告否認一項猥褻侵犯罪，案件在粉嶺裁判法院開審。<br />\n<br />\n事主X作供說，被告在按摩她大腿期間，撫摸她的私處，維持了大約一分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n辯方質疑她的作供，與在社交平台的帖文內容有出入，又質疑事主事後仍然和被告有來往。<br />\n<br />\n事主解釋，是因為想當事件沒有發生過。"},{"pid":"07e63b920a34534e490d355706d7e45b14a98a60","tid":837282,"uid":8187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T16:24:49.000Z","msg":"冇正確日期時間<br />\n但係又講得出細節？<br />\n冇人證物證<br />\n咁樣都有得告？<br />\n而加真係是但搵條女出黎求其講2句都可以搞到你成身屎<br />\n反正佢鳩up又冇罪<br />\n告唔告得入條女都乜事都冇<br />\n但人地就成世比人當強姦犯咁睇<br />\n女人？屌你老母啦"},{"pid":"30546f5a45dc032bc21d1f4010a8297e1a35186d","tid":837282,"uid":112988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T17:26:37.000Z","msg":"中一有咁多陰毛？"}]}